        <title>How to tap &quot;Enable links&quot; on iOS with soft keyboard present?</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[sylumer]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>You set an action group to show as the extended row. So no binding per se, just load the appropriate action group for use in the row.</p>
